title: CONVERSE RUBBER TRACKS
description:
Converse Rubber Tracks is a community-based professional recording studio in Brooklyn, NY. Emerging musicians of all genres can apply for free studio time. If selected, artists record at no cost while maintaining the rights to their own music. In addition to our Brooklyn studio, we partner with local recording studios around the world to provide free recording time for local musicians. 

Converse Rubber Tracks Live takes the studio experience to the live stage, as established headline acts invite Rubber Tracks alumni to support them during a series of exclusive free shows.
